@startuml
title Module Pipeline - Evaluation and Reporting
left to right direction

skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

actor "CLI user" as U

folder "data/exports" as EXP
folder "reports" as REPOUT

package "scripts" {
  component "run_evaluation.py" as EVALCLI
  component "run_graph_visualization.py" as VIZCLI
  component "run_event_timelines.py" as TIMECLI
  component "run_entity_analysis.py" as ENCLI
}

package "src.evaluation" {
  component "pipeline.py" as EP
  component "gold_loader.py" as GL
  component "metrics.py" as MT
  component "report_generator.py" as RG
}

package "src.reporting" {
  component "helpers.py" as HP
  component "plotly_viz.py" as PV
}

U --> EVALCLI
EVALCLI --> EP
EXP --> EP
EP --> GL
EP --> MT
EP --> RG
RG --> REPOUT

U --> VIZCLI
U --> TIMECLI
U --> ENCLI

VIZCLI --> PV
TIMECLI --> HP
ENCLI --> HP
HP --> REPOUT
PV --> REPOUT

note bottom
These modules consume pipeline outputs and generate analysis artifacts,
figures, and evaluation reports used in notebooks and final reporting.
end note

@enduml